sql:
SELECT county_name
FROM counties
ORDER BY county_name;

external_knowledge:
- Top-performing counties refer to those with the highest vaccination rates within each demographic category; 
- Vaccination rate is calculated as the number of people fully vaccinated divided by the total population, then multiplied by 100 to get a percentage; 
- Access and report frequencies are categorized as 'frequent' if the data has been accessed or reported more than once.
